data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT - WELCOME HOME - This beautifully designed 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience, with its close proximity to Tuloso Midway Schools, shopping, and restaurants. As you step inside you will discover a bright and inviting open layout that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The kitchen offers plenty of cabinet space, a walk-in pantry, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. This design is perfect for both daily living and entertaining friends and family. The master suite is a true retreat, boasting a spacious bedroom, walk-in closet, and an en-suite bathroom complete with a relaxing soaking tub and separate shower. Don't miss the opportunity to make this lovely home your own. Contact your favorite REALTOR® today to schedule a viewing.
